as Black Panther -- gets tested when he\'s drawn into a conflict that puts the fate of Wakanda and the entire world at risk. Faced with treachery and danger, the young king must rally his allies and release the full power of Black Panther to defeat his foes and secure the safety of his people.'),('Blackmail','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018','','','','A man secretly blackmails his wife and her lover when he discovers the affair.'),('Blockers','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14659754_p_v5_ab.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-03-10','R','01H','42M','Julie, Kayla and Sam are three high school seniors who make a pact to lose their virginity on prom night. Lisa, Mitchell and Hunter are three overprotective parents who flip out when they find out about their daughters\' plans. They soon join forces for a wild and chaotic quest to stop the girls from sealing the deal -- no matter what the cost.'),('Blumhouse\'s Truth or Dare','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14814469_p_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-04-13','PG-13','01H','40M','Olivia, Lucas and a group of their college friends travel to Mexico for one last getaway before graduation. While there, a stranger convinces one of the students to play a seemingly harmless game of truth or dare with the others. Once the game starts, it awakens something evil -- a demon which forces the friends to share dark secrets and confront their deepest fears. The rules are simple but wicked -- tell the truth or die, do the dare or die, and if you stop playing, you die.'),('Borg vs. McEnroe','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p13776100_v_v5_ay.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-09-07','R','01H','48M','The story of the rivalry between two 1980s tennis stars, the placid BjÃ¶rn Borg and the volatile John McEnroe.'),('Braguino','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydj