 Baptiste befriends the man and dog and accompanies them along their epic journey through harsh conditions and incredible acts of courage.'),('Sherlock Gnomes','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p13794695_p_v5_ac.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-03-23','PG','01H','26M','When Gnomeo and Juliet first arrive in London with their friends and family, their biggest concern is getting a new garden ready for spring. When everyone in the garden suddenly goes missing -- there\'s only one gnome to call -- Sherlock Gnomes. The famous detective and sworn protector of the city shows up with his sidekick Watson to investigate the case. The mystery soon leads the gnomes on a rollicking adventure as they meet all-new ornaments and explore an undiscovered side of London.'),('Silence','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','1971',NULL,'02H','09M','Two Portuguese priests go to Japan to help Christian sects, driven underground by a ruthless magistracy, to regain a foothold. Quickly drawn into a mire of persecution, the missionaries soon learn the fate of a mission decades earlier.'),('Super Troopers 2','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14477928_p_v5_ab.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-04-20','R','01H','43M','Fired for their previous shenanigans, former Vermont Highway Patrol officers Thorny, Farva, Rabbit, Foster and Mac get a shot at redemption from Capt. O\'Hagan and Gov. Jessan. The wacky quintet must provide law enforcement for a French Canadian town that\'s transitioning to U.S. sovereignty. Their unconventional methods soon get put to the test when they encounter a smarmy mayor, mischievous Mounties, a smuggling ring and a 1,300-pound bear.'),('Sympathy for the Devil','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p5976_v_v5_ab.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','1968',NULL,'01H','39M','Scenes from the Rolling Stones\' recording studio sessions are interspersed with footage of the Vietnam War.'),('The Cat Returns -- Studio Ghibli Fest 2018','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','','','01H','25M','A dapper feline takes a lucky schoolgirl on a magical adventure in the anime film \"The Cat Returns\"; dubbed in English on April 22 and April 25, and subtitled on April 23.'),('The Death of Stalin','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14589654_v_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-09-08','R','01H','47M','When tyrannical dictator Joseph Stalin dies in 1953, his parasitic cronies square off in a frantic power struggle to become the next Soviet leader. Among the contenders are the dweebish Georgy Malenkov, the wily Nikita Khrushchev and Lavrenti Beria -- the sadistic secret police chief. As they bumble, brawl and back-stab their way to the top, the question remains -- just who is running the government?'),('The Devil and Father Amorth','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p15076386_v_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-08-31',NULL,'01H','08M','Filmmaker William Friedkin follows the Rev. Gabriele Amorth as he performs an exorcism on a woman in Italy.'),('The Exorcist','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p6107_v_v5_ay.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','1973-12-26','R','02H','02M','One of the most profitable horror movies ever made, this tale of an exorcism is based loosely on actual events. When young Regan (Linda Blair) starts acting odd -- levitating, speaking in tongues -- her worried mother (Ellen Burstyn) seeks medical help, only to hit a dead end. A local priest (Jason Miller), however, thinks the girl may be seized by the devil. The priest makes a request to perform an exorcism, and the church sends in an expert (Max von Sydow) to help with the difficult job.'),('The IMAX VR: Justice League VR: Cyborg Flash, Wonder Woman','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq',NULL,NULL,'','',''),('The Killers','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p4181_v_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','1946-08-28',NULL,'01H','45M','Two hit men walk into a diner asking for a man called \"the Swede\" (Burt Lancaster). When the killers find the Swede, he\'s expecting them and doesn\'t put up a fight. Since the Swede had a life insurance policy, an investigator (Edmond O\'Brien), on a hunch, decides to look into the murder. As the Swede\'s past is laid bare, it comes to light that he was in love with a beautiful woman (Ava Gardner) who may have lured him into pulling off a bank robbery overseen by another man (Albert Dekker).'),('The Metropolitan Opera: Cendrillon Encore','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq',NULL,NULL,'03H','15M','Bertrand de Billy conducts mezzo-soprano Joyce DiDonato, mezzo-soprano Alice Coote, soprano Kathleen Kim and mezzo-soprano Stephanie Blythe in an encore performance of Massenet\'s \"Cendrillon.\"'),('The Miracle Season','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14953815_v_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-04-06','PG','01H','39M','Based on the inspiring true story of the West High School girl\'s volleyball team. After the tragic loss of star player Caroline \"Line\" Found in an accident, the remaining team players must band together under the guidance of their tough-love coach, Kathy Bresnahan, in hopes of winning the state championship.'),('The Rider','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14671211_p_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-05-20','R','01H','44M','After a riding accident leaves him unable to compete on the rodeo circuit, a young cowboy searches for a new purpose.'),('The Shape of Water','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14064584_v_v5_ad.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-08-31','R','02H','03M','Elisa is a mute, isolated woman who works as a cleaning lady in a hidden, high-security government laboratory in 1962 Baltimore. Her life changes forever