thing he wanted her to be. She sacrificed for him, worked to support his grandiose dreams, and put up with him for better or for worse. Then, one day she realized that after all she had done, another woman was reaping the lavish rewards. That\'s when Melinda lost it, and now she cannot let it go.'),('Unsane','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p14830399_p_v5_aa.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018-02-20','R','01H','38M','Sawyer Valentini relocates from Boston to Pennsylvania to escape from the man who\'s been stalking her for the last two years. While consulting with a therapist, Valentini unwittingly signs in for a voluntary 24-hour commitment to the Highland Creek Behavioral Center. Her stay at the facility soon gets extended when doctors and nurses begin to question her sanity. Sawyer now believes that one of the staffers is her stalker -- and she\'ll do whatever it takes to stay alive and fight her way out.'),('Veneno','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2018',NULL,'01H','36M','Jack Veneno becomes the most famous Dominican wrestler of all time and faces his archrival, Relampago Hernandez.'),('VR: Eagle Flight','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq',NULL,NULL,'','',''),('VR: Raw Data V1.1','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq',NULL,NULL,'','',''),('Wanderland','http://developer.tmsimg.com/assets/p15373362_v_v5_ab.jpg?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017',NULL,'01H','29M','Seeking an escape from his isolated life in New York, Alex accepts a mysterious invitation to house-sit a picturesque cottage on Long Island.'),('Where Is Kyra?','http://developer.tmsimg.com/tvbanners/generic/generic_tvbanners_v5.png?api_key=54jmnjmpmgek7ydjy7984zxq','2017-01-23',NULL,'01H','38M','A fragile woman is already stressed from a fast-paced world when her mother dies and sh